                    <span style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#363E3F;font-size:17px;'>I have read the Product Disclosure Sheet and I fully understood the contents of the Product Disclosure Sheet and my particular attention has been drawn to the essential information of the major features and limitations of which has been satisfactory explained to me.</span>
