            <ol style="margin-bottom:0in;list-style-type: lower-roman;">
                <li style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;'>
                    <span style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#363E3F;font-size:17px;'>I am aware that it is my pre-contractual duty of disclosure that I must exercise reasonable care not to misrepresent i.e. to give false answers/information when answering any questions asked by DearTime and that I am to answer the questions fully and accurately/correctly;</span>
                    <p class="bm" style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#363E3F;font-size:17px;'><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#404040;'>Saya mengetahui bahawa adalah menjadi kewajipan pendedahan prakontrak saya bahawa saya mestilah mengambil langkah yang sewajarnya untuk tidak membuat salah nyata, iaitu memberi jawapan/maklumat palsu apabila menjawab sebarang soalan yang ditanya oleh DearTime dan saya hendaklah menjawab soalan dengan lengkap dan dengan tepat/betul.</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#404040;'>:</span></p>
                    <p style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#363E3F;font-size:17px;'><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>我知道我的合同前透露义务是我必须谨慎及不被误导，即在回答任何</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>DearTime</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>提出的问题给出错误的回答</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>或</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>信息，并且我将完整和准确</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>/</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>正确地回答这些问题；</span></p>
                </li>
                <li style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;'>
                    <span style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#363E3F;font-size:17px;'>I have read and understood the contents of my application including all warnings and notices therein and I have fully and accurately answered all the questions in this application and the other questions asked by DearTime, if any, after having fully read and understood the questions.</span>
                    <p class="bm" style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#363E3F;font-size:17px;'><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#404040;'>Saya telah membaca dan memahami isi kandungan permohonan ini termasuk semua peringatan dan notis di dalamnya dan saya telah menjawab semua soalan dalam permohonan ini dan soalan lain yang ditanya oleh DearTime, jika ada, dengan lengkap dan tepat selepas membaca dan memahami soalan-soalan tersebut sepenuhnya.</span></p>
                    <p style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#363E3F;font-size:17px;'><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>我已经阅读并理解了我的申请内容，其中包括所有的警告和注意事项，并且在阅读并理解了所有问题之后，我已经完整准确地回答了该申请中的所有问题以及</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>DearTime</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'></span></p>
                </li>
                <li style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;'>
                    <span style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#363E3F;font-size:17px;'>I am aware that I must inform DearTime of any change to the answers given in this application if the change occurred after I have submitted the application but before the contract is entered into.</span>
                    <p class="bm" style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#363E3F;font-size:17px;'><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#404040;'></span>Saya mengetahui bahawa saya mesti memberitahu DearTime mengenai sebarang perubahan pada jawapan yang telah diberikan dalam permohonan ini jika perubahan tersebut berlaku selepas saya menyerahkan permohonan ini tetapi sebelum kontrak dimeterai.</p>
                    <p style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#363E3F;font-size:17px;'><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>我知道在我已经提交了申请但合约生效之前，如本申请中给的答案有任何改变，我必须通知</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>DearTime</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>。</span></p>
