                    <span style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#363E3F;font-size:17px;'>I agree that neither DearTime nor its employees shall be liable for any direct or indirect loss or damage due to my inaccuracy or incompleteness in the personal information provided to DearTime and shall include but shall not be limited to personal details of transactions with or through DearTime whether within or outside Malaysia involving any party.</span>
