                    <p style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#363E3F;font-size:17px;'><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>我同意由于我在提供给</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>DearTime</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>的个人信息中的不准确或不完整，</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>DearTime</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>及其员工均不对任何直接或间接的损失或损害负责，并且包括但不限于与</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>DearTime</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>或通过</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>DearTime</span><span style='font-size:17px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#363E3F;'>在马来西亚境内或境外涉及任何一方所进行交易的个人详细信息。</span></p>
